            "text": "rahmatan min rabbika innahu huwa l-samiʿu l-ʿalimu"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 44,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "rabbi l-samawati wal-ardi wama baynahuma in kuntum muqinina"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 44,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "la ilaha illa huwa yuh'yi wayumitu rabbukum warabbu abaikumu l-awalina"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 44,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "bal hum fi shakkin yalʿabuna"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 44,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "fa-ir'taqib yawma tati l-samau bidukhanin mubinin"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 44,
