            "text": "yaghsha l-nasa hadha ʿadhabun alimun"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 44,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "rabbana ik'shif ʿanna l-ʿadhaba inna mu'minuna"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 44,
