            "text": "anna lahumu l-dhik'ra waqad jaahum rasulun mubinun"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 44,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "thumma tawallaw ʿanhu waqalu muʿallamun majnunun"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 44,
            "verse": 15,
